{"tid":175004,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"免費教結他","createTime":"2017-03-27T08:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T11:24:46.000Z","uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4567537da955d67899bf899ad2b8ac0154db9607","tid":175004,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"之前開過 post 話教完之前果兩個後會再收，而家第二 round<br />\n<br />\n戴定頭盔先，由於我講明免費，所以唔涉及乜野商業野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身係音樂教育 degree holder，係全職 freelance musician，唔係果種掃兩下chord 就話自己識彈出黎教果種。 <br />\n<br />\n教左一段時間，發現最有 passion 學但又最冇能力學既係在職貧窮既人（即是大多數巴絲打既年紀） <br />\n所以希望可以幫到吓大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有幾個要求： <br />\n<br />\n只教四堂免費 <br />\n<br />\n時間地點要就我，近荃灣西鐵站 <br />\n<br />\n唔包括我本身既學生 <br />\n<br />\n我都係在職貧窮 JJ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 音樂人都要食飯，同埋我本身都有一堆收錢既學生。所以為左唔做爛市保障同行，我只收兩個人免費，過左果四堂後我會再收下 round <br />\n<br />\n如果想正常地比學費學我當然歡迎，但都為保障同行，我唔公開我真正收費，呢點私下傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢四堂只係想教到你可以有咁上下既理解能力去自學落去，for beginner 為主 <br />\n當然結果你有興趣，我好鼓勵你繼續學落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意請 add telegram : <a href=\"https://t.me/musicmanctc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmusicmanctc&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4b42ac16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/musicmanctc</a>"},{"pid":"18830461a32c54f1feb6b2f9473055f2e30de550","tid":175004,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"我會以同我 pm 既人作準，先 pm 果個會先覆，所以如果我未覆你，即是你前面果個我未傾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我係巴打，呢個 ac 係我同一位絲打朋友共用的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dce369654571047c29b82f22e4f34fd4f8163d","tid":175004,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f8f8715571d16f99be9888a73d785a067bf935","tid":175004,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"收左一個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a775151dcc26128b91bc825b57d367999579d4d7","tid":175004,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"月堇絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f2f7b6854be8f19c2d79ddbe9670b4b1361d27","tid":175004,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}